      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl293a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>Nashville</name>
                     <date>July 24 1849</date>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Mr <name>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>A</abbr>
                           <expan>Adam</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                           <orig>Ferguson</orig>
                           <reg>Fergusson</reg>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Excuse me for troubling you with this note but as I wish to start East about the first of August will want all the funds that I can possibly get you will therefore <choice>
                  <orig>doe</orig>
                  <reg>do</reg>
               </choice> us the <choice>
                  <orig>favour</orig>
                  <reg>favor</reg>
               </choice> to remit the amount of your account</p>
            <p>Times have been so hard here this summer that we find ourselves almost unable to make our arrangements for the fall trade</p>
            <p>we hope you will find it convenient to comply with our request and that we will receive a <unclear>centimment</unclear> of you favour</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>
                  <choice>
                     <orig>Verry</orig>
                     <reg>very</reg>
                  </choice> respectfully <choice>
                     <abbr>&amp;c</abbr>
                     <expan>and etcetera</expan>
                  </choice>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <unclear>T L Legger</unclear>
               </signed>
               <add place="bottom of page">Amount of <unclear>owe</unclear> $ 57 25</add>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl293b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>A Ferguson <choice>
                        <abbr>Esq</abbr>
                        <expan>Esquire</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>Carthage</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Tenn</abbr>
                           <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
